  { q: "Sofia Professional vs Accento — what's the tier split?", a: "Two different product categories rather than two tiers. <b>Sofia Professional 30\"</b> is Fulgor Milano's mainstream US wall oven — standard 30\" cabinet cutout, US-convention built-in dimensions, pro-grade Italian engineering with Fulgor's signature convection architecture and control platform. Sofia competes at the premium Italian tier alongside Bertazzoni Professional and ILVE's mainstream 30\". <b>Accento 24\"</b> is the compact European-sized category — different cabinet cutout, different cavity size, different application positioning (ADU + guest house + compact condo rather than primary kitchen). Both products share Fulgor's control platform family and parts-chain infrastructure but differ in cavity-specific components (bake elements sized for the respective cavity volumes, for example)." },
