    <p>For LA service, Fulgor Milano parts run through Schaumburg IL distribution with typical 4-7 day lead on common service components and 7-14 days on specialty Italian-factory-specific parts. Accento 24" compact-category parts sometimes run longer lead times because of the lower US install volume for the compact category versus mainstream 30" Sofia parts.</p>
